<i>kimi ga hai ta shiroi iki ga
The white breath you exhale</i>
<i>Matsushige Yutaka</i>

7
00:00:28,243 --> 00:00:30,694
<i>kimi ga hai ta shiroi iki ga
The white breath you exhale</i>
<i> </i>

8
